{"lemma":"زُلْفَة","slug":"زُلْفَة","root":"ز.ل.ف","root_slug":"ز-ل-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/ز-ل-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"زُلْفَة","root":"زلف","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n18006","n18014","n18015"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B2%D9%8F%D9%84%D9%92%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"nearness, proximity, neighborliness literally and figuratively","tags":["archaic"],"examples":[{"text":"وَإِنَّ لَهُ، عِنْدَنَا لَزُلْفَى وَحُسْنَ مَآبٍ","english":"And to him and to us there is neighborliness"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"those who are near, thy neighbours, or those who have a higher rank in relation to something","tags":["archaic"],"examples":[{"text":"مَا نَعْبُدُهُمْ إِلَّا لِيُقَرِّبُونَآ إِلَى ٱللَّهِ زُلْفَىٰٓ","english":"We worship them not but to come closer to God’s intimate circle."},{"text":"وَمَآ أَمْوَٰلُكُمْ وَلَآ أَوْلَـٰدُكُم بِٱلَّتِى تُقَرِّبُكُمْ عِندَنَا زُلْفَىٰٓ","english":"And neither your riches nor your children are what bring you close to the intimate circle."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"grovelling, flattery by coming close in a respect","tags":["archaic"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a period time comprising a commencing portion of either night or day","tags":["archaic"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"singulative of زَلَف (zalaf, “mother-of-pearl-shell”)","tags":["archaic","form-of","obsolete","singulative"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"See there."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n18006","headword_ar":"زلّفهُ","root":"zlf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (O, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tazoliyfN","text_ar":"تَزْلِيفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did it previously,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beforehand;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a thing; (IAar, O, TA;) as, for instance, an evil action; (O, TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalafahu","text_ar":"زَلَفَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (IAar, TA;) syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asolafahu","text_ar":"اَسْلَفَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qad~amahu","text_ar":"قَدَّمَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IAar, O, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zl~f","text_ar":"زلّف"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAsa","text_ar":"النَّاسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He disquieted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"agitated, the people, step by step:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, Z, O, TA:) accord. to Z, said of a guide. (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zl~f fiY","text_ar":"زلّف فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hadiyvihi","text_ar":"حَدِيثِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (inf. n. as above, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He added,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exaggerated, in his discourse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"narration;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, O, K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*r~f","text_ar":"ذرّف"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IDrd, O.)"}],"source_refs":["O","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n18014","headword_ar":"زُلْفَةٌ","root":"zlf","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurobapN","text_ar":"قُرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Nearness, with respect to rank, degree,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"station"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, Mgh, O, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulofaY","text_ar":"زُلْفَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, O, Msb,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalafN","text_ar":"زَلَفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IDrd, O, K.) [It would seem that it means also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Nearness with respect to place"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"situation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"for SM immediately adds,] hence, in the Kur [lxvii. 27],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falam~aA raA^awohu zulofapF","text_ar":"فَلَمَّا رَاَوْهُ زُلْفَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", [as though meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"But when they shall see it in a state of nearness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but] Zj says that the meaning is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but when they shall see it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(i. e. the punishment)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"near"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qariybFA","text_ar":"قَرِيبًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"): and several authors say that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulofapN","text_ar":"زُلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is sometimes used in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qariybN","text_ar":"قَرِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as is stated in the 'Ináyeh. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Station, rank, grade,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"degree;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulofaY","text_ar":"زُلْفَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K, TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalofN","text_ar":"زَلْفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TS, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalafN","text_ar":"زَلَفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA:) pl. of the first"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulafN","text_ar":"زُلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, * TA:) or (K) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulofaY","text_ar":"زُلْفَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a quasi-inf. n.; (S, K;) and such it is in the saying in the Kur [xxxiv. 36],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wamaA","text_ar":"وَمَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amowaAlukumo walaA A^awolaAdukumo biA@l~atiY tuqar~ibukumo EinodinaA zulofaY","text_ar":"اَمْوَالُكُمْ وَلَا اَوْلَادُكُمْ بِا@لَّتِى تُقَرِّبُكُمْ عِنْدِنَا زُلْفَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", as though meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@zodilaAfFA","text_ar":"ا@زْدِلَافًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And neither your riches nor your children are what will bring you near to us in advancement:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but here it may be well rendered,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in station"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) accord. to Ibn- 'Arafeh,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulofaY","text_ar":"زُلْفَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bringing very near:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) the saying of Ibn-El-Tilimsánee that it is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulofapN","text_ar":"زُلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is very strange, and unknown; the correct pl. of this last word being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulafN","text_ar":"زُلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (MF, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A portion"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the first part"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) of the night, (S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whether small"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"large:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so accord. to Th: or, accord. to Akh, of the night absolutely: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulafN","text_ar":"زُلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulafaAtN","text_ar":"زُلَفَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulufaAtN","text_ar":"زُلُفَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulofaAtN","text_ar":"زُلْفَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulafN","text_ar":"زُلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hours,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"periods,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAEaAt","text_ar":"سَاعَات"},{"kind":"text","text":",) of the night,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"commencing from the daytime,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hours,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"periods,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the daytime,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"commencing from the night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and its sing. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulofapN","text_ar":"زُلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wazulafFA mina All~ayoli","text_ar":"وَزُلَفًا مِنَ اللَّيْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [xi. 116], means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And at sunset and nightfall"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magorib","text_ar":"مَغْرِب"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ei$aA='","text_ar":"عِشَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (Zj, TA:) some read ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulufFA","text_ar":"زُلُفًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with two dammehs; which may be a sing., like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HulumN","text_ar":"حُلُمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulofapN","text_ar":"زُلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"busurN","text_ar":"بُسُرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"busurapN","text_ar":"بُسُرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"s","text_ar":"س"},{"kind":"text","text":"in each: [but this is not a parallel instance; for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"busurN","text_ar":"بُسُرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a coll. gen. n. of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"busurapN","text_ar":"بُسُرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the n. un., and the latter is not of the same measure as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulofapN","text_ar":"زُلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] and some read ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulofFA","text_ar":"زُلْفًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is a pl. [or rather coll. gen. n.] of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulofapN","text_ar":"زُلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dur~N","text_ar":"دُرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dur~apN","text_ar":"دُرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;) or pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaliyfN","text_ar":"زَلِيفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurobN","text_ar":"قُرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qariybN","text_ar":"قَرِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gurobN","text_ar":"غُرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariybN","text_ar":"غَرِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and some read ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulofaY","text_ar":"زُلْفَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", in which the alif [written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is a denotative of the fem. gender. (K, TA.)       -A2-  See also the next paragraph."}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","O","Msb","K","TA","TS","Zj"]},{"entry_id":"n18015","headword_ar":"زَلَفَةٌ","root":"zlf","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A full"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reservoir of water such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSonaEap","text_ar":"مَصْنَعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) pl. [or rather coll. gen. n.] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalafN","text_ar":"زَلَفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) so, accord. to Sh, in the trad. mentioned voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zilofN","text_ar":"زِلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalafN","text_ar":"زَلَفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"full watering-troughs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) as pl. [or coll. gen. n.] of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalafapN","text_ar":"زَلَفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a full watering-trough."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bowl such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHofap","text_ar":"صَحْفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulofapN","text_ar":"زُلْفَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Ibn-'Abbád, K;) of which the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zulafN","text_ar":"زُلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a full"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHofap","text_ar":"صَحْفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and its pl. [or coll. gen. n.] is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalafN","text_ar":"زَلَفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Lth, TA.) Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A green"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vessel of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ij~aAnap","text_ar":"اـِجَّانَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) so says AO: pl. [or coll. gen. n.] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalafN","text_ar":"زَلَفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mazaAlifu","text_ar":"مَزَالِفُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"likewise signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"green"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajaAjiyn","text_ar":"اَجَاجِين"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. as an anomalous pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalafapN","text_ar":"زَلَفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalafN","text_ar":"زَلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$aAbihu","text_ar":"مَشَابِهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$abahN","text_ar":"شَبَهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; both, also, mentioned on the authority of AO. (TA.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mother-of-pearl-'shell,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an oyster-shell;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SadafapN","text_ar":"صَدَفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) Kt says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alz~alafap","text_ar":"الزَّلَفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the trad. mentioned above voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zilofN","text_ar":"زِلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has been expl. as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaArap","text_ar":"مَحَارَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sadafap","text_ar":"صَدَفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but he adds, I know not this explanation, unless a pool of water be called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mHArp","text_ar":"محارة"},{"kind":"text","text":"because the water returns ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaHuwru","text_ar":"يَحُورُ"},{"kind":"text","text":") to it and collects in it. (TA.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A smooth rock:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) so, too, said to mean in the same trad.: and some read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alzlqp","text_ar":"الزلقة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rugged ground."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Swept ground."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An even part of a soft mountain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) Pl. (K) [or rather coll. gen. n.] in all these senses (TA) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalafN","text_ar":"زَلَفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b4-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zilofN","text_ar":"زِلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b5-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mirror:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K: [in the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaroA^apu","text_ar":"المَرْاَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is put in the place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmiroA=pu","text_ar":"المِرْا=ةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalaqapN","text_ar":"زَلَقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] mentioned by IB on the authority of Aboo-'Amr Ez-Záhid, and by Sgh on that of Ks: and so, too, it is said to mean in the trad. mentioned above; the earth being likened thereto because of its evenness and cleanness: (TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"face thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) as is said by IAar. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA"]}]}}